# Pentagon Purpose Repair - 2026-05-22

Status: verified_by_live_ui
Verifier: Codex via /Applications/Pentagon.app Computer Use plus Claude CLI MCP scope checks

## Scope Finding

Claude CLI now has Pentagon MCP connectivity, but the available
`patch_document` tool is caller-scoped. With the current token it patches
Priya's own Purpose only. It cannot patch arbitrary peer agent Purposes by
agent id.

Durable rule:
Cross-agent Purpose repair requires either exact-DM live activation of the
target agent or a target-scoped token/session. `send_message` delivery by MCP is
not activation proof.

## MCP Delivery Failure

At approximately 2026-05-22T18:02Z, Priya-scoped MCP `send_message` delivered
self-patch directives to Avery, Sofia, Sasha, Theo, Maya, Quinn, Rowan, Riley,
and Grace. A later `read_messages` poll found directive-only conversations:

~~~text
0/9 PURPOSE_PATCHED, 0/9 PURPOSE_BLOCKED, 9/9 SILENT
~~~

Verdict:
MCP `send_message` is context delivery, not activation proof.

