## Misroute Finding

Before exact-DM verification, coordinate-based clicks landed some Purpose
instructions in the wrong thread after the DM list reordered. Example:

~~~text
INTERPRETER_BLOCKED Sofia request landed in Avery's conversation; routed to Sofia DM ...
~~~

And Grace's thread contained an earlier misrouted Sasha instruction. These are
not counted as target Purpose proof. Exact search plus selected-header
verification is now the required gate for UI-driven agent operations.

## Remaining Open Gate

Purpose coverage is repaired for the core team, but T5 autonomy is not closed
until the Theo -> Maya handoff activates Maya and produces an implementation
commit without Codex fallback.
